      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fairview%2C_Dutchess_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Violet Avenue, or NY‑9G, cuts through Fairview’s center, providing a north–south artery.",
