      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fairview%2C_Dutchess_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The western side of Fairview hosts part of Marist University’s campus, while Dutchess Community College lies on the eastern flank.",
