      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fairview%2C_Dutchess_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Fairview is included in the Kiryas Joel–Poughkeepsie–Newburgh metropolitan area and the larger New York–Newark–Bridgeport combined statistical area.",
